==English==
===Etymology===
From Turkish ''[[urdu]]'', [[camp]].  Same root as [[horde]].

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Urdu'''
# A [[Indo-Iranian]] language with native speakers mainly in [[Pakistan]] and [[India]].

